task.summary: Added tests for Differences in DataAggregation
Refactored ItemCounter and some Canonical code to aid readability

Added some comparitor tests and DataAggregatorParams to easily change aggregation parameters.
ComparitorString is now an interface and ComparitorStringable takes an implementation of a CoparitorString.
Added tests for COmparitorCriterion and ComparitorCriterionSubject
Added CanonicalStringMaker as an abstraction for getting mode strings
Added CanonicalStringMakerTest as an abstraction for testing multiple Canonicals. Added equivalent tests
Added NullData as a factory in DataDefinitions as single source of null data items. Changed Canonicals to return NullData.nullType when no data passed. Added tests for remaining canonicals.
Added random data size to CanonicalFactTest
Added aggregator tests for Criterion and Location
Adjusted CanonicalCommentModeTest in light of changing CanonicalCommentMode to display number of comments as canonical comment
Added a bit ore variability to random locations in AggregatorLocationTest
Added comparator tests for Authors and Criteria
Separated out LocationServices as a separate package to allow easier plug in of different providers
In the process of splitting out database from android implementation
Separated out implementation of Android SQLite Db from Db code into plugins directory
Splir out LocationProviders and Persistence as plugins
Split out as much of Android views as I could into UiPlugins

MESSAGE.value: Added test for ComparitorDate
Added test for ComparitorFactLabel, ComparitorLocationName
Added tests for remaining comparitors
Added test for CanonicalAuthor
Added CanonicalStringMaker as an abstraction for getting mode strings
Added CanonicalStringMakerTest as an abstraction for testing multiple Canonicals. Added equivalent tests
Added NullData as a factory in DataDefinitions as single source of null data items. Changed Canonicals to return NullData.nullType when no data passed. Added tests for remaining canonicals.
Added random data size to CanonicalFactTest
Adding test for DataAggregatorImpl
Added test for DataAggregatorImpl
Added some aggregator tests
Added aggregator tests for Criterion and Location
Added aggregator test for facts
Adjusted CanonicalCommentModeTest in light of changing CanonicalCommentMode to display number of comments as canonical comment
Added a bit ore variability to random locations in AggregatorLocationTest
Added comparator tests for Authors and Criteria
Added comparator tests for Comments
Added som comparator tests
Separated out LocationServices as a separate package to allow easier plug in of different providers
In the process of splitting out database from android implementation
Removed Cursor from DbTableRow construction
Separated out implementation of Android SQLite Db from Db code into plugins directory
Some code cleanup
Splir out LocationProviders and Persistence as plugins
Split out as much of Android views as I could into UiPlugins
